Name: bronchiectasis 1
Definition: A bronchiectasis that has_material_basis_in mutation in the gene encoding the beta subunit of the epithelial sodium channel on chromosome 16p12.

Name: bronchiectasis 2
Definition: A bronchiectasis that has_material_basis_in mutation in the gene encoding the alpha subunit of the epithelial sodium channel.

Name: bronchiectasis 3
Definition: A bronchiectasis that has_material_basis_in mutation in the gene encoding the gamma subunit of the epithelial sodium channel.
